# PayCash Quick Deployment Guide

## Prerequisites
- GitHub repo: https://github.com/wongstephen370-boop/PAYCASHH
- DigitalOcean account
- Vercel account

## Backend Deployment (DigitalOcean)

1. Push to GitHub
```bash
git add .
git commit -m "PayCash production deployment setup"
git push origin main
